<br>
Rod of Mystical Transvergence also drops in the Ssraeshza Temple off the same kind of mobs. We got only one of those.<br>
<br>
During our 3 or so hours on the first floor poking around, we got the 3 mage spells, an a bunch of chanter, shammy, cleric, druid, and bard spells as well. Probably close to a dozen all told. No other loot though - the other drops were no drop shissar parts (eggs, scales, venom sack, etc), a nodrop idol with no stats apparently for a quest off the Commander near the 2nd floor entrance, and thats about it. Some people were wondering if the zone has all the items populated as yet...or perhaps they are on the higher floors... At any rate, the place was fun. You will need a group to go in, and the spawn timers are very erratic...stuff also warps around a lot...<br>
<br>
Am down to needing Veil of Elements (haven't seen it drop in Fungus Grove yet but have heard 3 people getting it now), and need the two level 60 spells (no idea on drop location, but the working theory is an upper floor in the temple where the other one's dropped)... <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=30883">
